comment._content: This is a Burnelli CBY-3. This shows parts missing that were being refurbished in 1959. See more great photos and the man who worked on her here: [ www.beaconfieldairport.com/airportscrapbook.html ] Past halfway down the page. See more of Burnelli's planes at: www.burnelliaircraft.com/
